    <p>
        EO.ComboBox greatly enhance the built-in HTML/ASP.NET ComboBox. Feature highlights include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Fully customizable through both standard .NET properties and CSS;</li>
        <li>Built in Office 2003, Office 2007 and Windows 7 style ComboBox ready to be used out of box;</li>
        <li>Ability to assign and customize icons for each item as well as icon for the selected item;</li>
        <li>Full keyboard navigation support;</li>
        <li>Drop down template allows you to place any other control inside the ComboBox's drop down;</li>
        <li>Extensive expand and collapse animation effect;</li>
        <li>Hint text feature allows you to display a prompting text when no item is selected;</li>
        <li>Complete client side JavaScript interface;</li>
    </ul>
